Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:35.41,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Sometimes I wonder again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.63,0:22:40.93,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}跨越數千年 接力棒傳到我們手中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.93,0:22:45.43,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}因漫長道路而目眩 天旋地轉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:51.18,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定有尚未發現的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:55.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}時刻都在這樣思索 思索
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:00.90,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不懼失敗 反覆嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:06.81,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}哭著笑著 追尋光明
